Description: Core C++ engine for glmbayes: envelope-based iid samplers, Gibbs
    building blocks, and optional OpenCL. Developer backend for glmbayes,
    lmebayes, and extensions. End users should use glmbayes for lm/glm
    modelling.
License: GPL-2
URL: https://github.com/knygren/glmbayesCore
